msgstr "你可以使用命令 /language 切换此 mod 的语言。"

#: src/game/server/gamecontext.cpp:2963
msgid "If your language is not available, you can help with translation (/help translate)."
msgstr "如果您的语言还不可用，您可以帮助翻译（详见 /help translate）。"

#: src/game/server/gamecontext.cpp:3053
msgid "You will now see all tees on this server, no matter the distance"
msgstr "你现在能看到服务器上的所有 Tee，无论距离"

